org.apache.poi.hwmf.record

Class HwmfFill.WmfStretchBlt

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwmf.record.HwmfFill.WmfStretchBlt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, HwmfRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HwmfFill.WmfBitBlt
    Enclosing class:
    HwmfFill 

    public static class HwmfFill.WmfStretchBlt
extends java.lang.Object
implements HwmfRecord
    The META_STRETCHBLT record specifies the transfer of a block of pixels according to a raster operation, with possible expansion or contraction. The destination of the transfer is the current output region in the playback device context. There are two forms of META_STRETCHBLT, one which specifies a bitmap as the source, and the other which uses the playback device context as the source. Definitions follow for the fields that are the same in the two forms of META_STRETCHBLT are defined below. The subsections that follow specify the packet structures of the two forms of META_STRETCHBLT. The expansion or contraction is performed according to the stretching mode currently set in the playback device context, which MUST be a value from the StretchMode.(Meta_STRETCHBLT记录指定根据格栅操作的像素块的传输，并可能进行扩展或收缩。传输的目的地是播放设备上下文中的当前输出区域。Meta_STRETCHBLT有两种形式，一种指定位图作为源，另一种使用播放设备上下文作为源。以下是Meta_STRETCHBLT两种形式中相同的字段的定义。下面的小节指定了两种形式的Meta_STRETCHBLT的数据包结构。根据播放设备上下文中当前设置的拉伸模式进行扩展或收缩，拉伸模式必须是来自StretchMode的值。)

      • rasterOperation

        protected HwmfTernaryRasterOp rasterOperation
        A 32-bit unsigned integer that defines how the source pixels, the current brush in the playback device context, and the destination pixels are to be combined to form the new image. This code MUST be one of the values in the Ternary Raster Operation Enumeration(一个32位无符号整元，定义如何组合源像素、播放设备上下文中的当前画笔和目标像素以形成新图像。此代码必须是三元网格操作列举中的值之一)
